channel.title: Pesterd|Eli ---- Retired RSCStake Admin and Founder
channel.description:
SOMEONE ELSE WILL BE TAKING OVER THE ADVERTISING
Well its been a long time.
Dear My fellow RSCStakers, Its that part of a life cycle that forces a man or women to stop whatever childish things that they are doing and must move on. That time my friends, in NOW. I have been doing poorly in school and that is not the way my parents raised me to be. I was born to be a College drop out and I will be ending that thought and am officially retiring as RSCStake Administrator.
/*** * Thank You * Block */
Daniel/Sythetic=The founder and friend of whom I have had many joyous times with and although none of you newer members have known him I am sure everyone would have like him
Chase= My favorite friend in the whole entire RSC community. 'Nuff Said :P (MSN is always fun with you)
Dallas= A great and true friend, Ill miss those amazing stories of you getting blazed with Dan.
I wish all of the aforementioned people the best of luck in everything they do.
For everyone that I did not mention. It does NOT mean I forgot about you. I remember you all with good hearts but simply didnt want to spend hours on end typing my love stories for all of you.
The mods and admins, all of whom have made my RSCStake experience an enjoyable one.
I wish everyone the best of luck in everything you do.
Thank you for the good times, Eli - Retired RSCStake Administrator and Founder
I will miss you all: Contact me!! fafus331@hotmail.com
